@node Main "GuideToTeX Documentation"

This file describes @{b}GuideToTeX 1.01@{ub}, a set of ARexx programs used to convert
an  AmigaGuide  file  into a TeX source file, suitable for typesetting with
TeX and showing/printing via ShowDVI/DVIPrint (part of PasTeX).

                             TABLE OF CONTENTS

	@{"Distribution and disclaimer" link dist}
	@{"Introduction" link intro}
	@{"System requirements" link sysreq}

	@{"GuideToTeX.rexx" link guidetotex}
	@{"GuideToDVI.rexx" link guidetodvi}
	@{"Provided headers" link provheaders}
	@{"FAQs and hints" link FAQ}

	@{"History" link hist}
	@{"Known problems" link probs}
	@{"Credits" link credits}
	@{"Contacting the author" link contact}
@endnode

